---

<div class="w-full xl:px-0 md:px-[0px] md:pt-[70px] pt-[40px] px-[20px]">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between md:gap-30 mb-4 md:mb-20 md:px-4"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-[28px] md:text-[35px] md:text-4xl font-heading leading-[120%] mb-4 gradient-text w-full md:w-4/12"
      >
        Mid Corporate Lending
      </h2>
      <p data-reveal class="fade-up font-normal text-[17px] w-full md:w-8/12">
        We empower India’s mid-sized and emerging enterprises with a fully digital, institution-grade credit infrastructure. Through our integrated suite — <span class="font-bold">Artemis</span> for loan onboarding and booking and <span class="font-bold">CredIQ</span> for credit and risk intelligence — we streamline the entire credit deployment process. 


      </p>
